title: Is this the "list of names" that Gislin Maxwell made?
subtitle: A list of dozens of Facebook names was provided in connection with the Jeffrey Epstein case of sex trafficking.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The Facebook list of public figures was part of a "unsealed" list of names kept by Gislin Maxwell, who was accused of facilitating sexual abuse of minors by Jeffrey Epstein.
